# Use cases regarding Router as Firewall 

1. No Threat Intelligence or Signature-Based Blocking 
2. Url or Web filtering 
3. No vpn ( functionlaites) 
4. IPS/IDS absence 
5. Logs()
6. Non-Compliance 
7. Network segmentation 
8. Performance 

2. Routers Can't Replace Enterprise-Grade Controls
